# The output indicates that the stone furnace has been successfully placed at the position (1.0, 1.0) and currently has 5 units of coal as fuel. However, it is showing a status of "NO_INGREDIENTS," which means it does not have any iron ore to smelt.

# Now, I need to insert the iron ore into the furnace to start the smelting process. 

# I will insert all 10 units of iron ore into the stone furnace.

insert_item(Prototype.IronOre, 'stone-furnace', quantity=10)  # Insert all 10 units of iron ore into the furnace.
